description: DynamicBlerTarget: Table storing dynamic BLER target configuration parameters for specific cells at a given time.  dateTime: Timestamp of the configuration; Area_Name: Name of the area; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell; Id2: Redundant cell identifier; Id3: Ancillary identifier (currently constant); vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format; DynamicBlerTarget.dynamicBlerTargetId: Unique ID of the BLER target configuration; DynamicBlerTarget.dlActivitySubscrDelay: Downlink activity subscription delay (in seconds); DynamicBlerTarget.dlAiLaCellRankingUpdatePeriod: Downlink AI/LA cell ranking update period (in seconds).
